{"type":"answer","id":12276,"parentType":"question","parentId":2661,"uid":2149,"contents":"《行路难（其一）》李白<br>\n<br>\n金樽清酒斗十千，玉盘珍羞直万钱。<br>\n<br>\n停杯投箸不能食，拔剑四顾心茫然。<br>\n<br>\n欲渡黄河冰塞川，将登太行雪满山。<br>\n<br>\n闲来垂钓碧溪上，忽复乘舟梦日边。<br>\n<br>\n行路难！行路难！多歧路，今安在？<br>\n<br>\n长风破浪会有时，直挂云帆济沧海。<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180916/d52873a0d6a412f4b330e94c4a7853b4.PNG\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180916/d52873a0d6a412f4b330e94c4a7853b4.PNG\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/answer/20180916/d52873a0d6a412f4b330e94c4a7853b4.PNG\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-09-16","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":0}